From 0bbbd0bdd28e54a9f68836150e81769e50587708 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: seroxdesign <sherifcherfa@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 18:04:14 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] feat: add configurable electricity cost settings with
 currency selection

Replace hardcoded PLN cost with user-configurable rate and currency.
Adds electricity cost configuration to the Config page (System tab)
with a 24-currency dropdown, and shows cost breakdown on the Usage page.

Backend:
- Add electricity_rate/currency to PersistedConfig and /studio/settings
- Include total_cost, rate, currency in /lifetime-metrics response
- Add /usage/cost endpoint with hourly and daily cost estimates

Frontend:
- Dashboard metric bar uses configurable rate/currency from API
- Config page System tab: rate input + currency dropdown (24 ISO tickers)
- Usage page: total cost card + cost breakdown section

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
